%F A206917 a(n) = (3/8)*2^(n+floor((n+1)/2)).
%F A206917 a(n) = 8*a(n-2) for n>3. G.f.: -x*(4*x^2+3*x+1) / (8*x^2-1). - _Colin Barker_, May 31 2013
%e A206917 a(0) = 0, since there is no binary palindrome 2^(-1) <= p < 2^0;
